Body: Next Steps Updated: I am waiting for the customer's response to find out if the issue is resolved before closing this ticket.
Next Steps Updated: Troubleshoot the connection profile to ensure the customer has enough permission to scan data.

What We've Learned Updated: The exchange On-premise is no longer collecting data because the customer migrated to Office365.
Some jobs that used to work with Exchange On-prem are not supported on Exchange Online, like the HUB Metrics group.
The customer extensively used this "HUB Metrics" group to collect data and is now looking for an alternative.
